body:
I was just now playing ARAM, and I&#039;m not sure when this started happening but I think it happened after every kill. So after every kill a siren, similar to a tornado siren, would go off for a little bit. At first I just brushed it off as my sound system acting up but then the gizmos shopkeeper said, &quot;That was just the wind...right?&quot; Which is something he&#039;s never said before...
Then I remembered what the Iceborn ghost said, &quot;When you hear the alarm, it means the watchers have returned.&quot;
I googled this after the game and saw nothing on it so I decided to make this post. Most likely rito has been deleting all the posts inquiring about it because they are working with the watchers and want ignorance among the summoners. Quickly then, tell me, have the watchers returned?

